programme.title: Cosmic Vistas: Landing on Mars

programme.title: Cosmic Vistas: The Hot Zone

programme.title: Cosmic Vistas: Cosmic Rays

programme.title: Cosmic Vistas: Fermi Paradox
programme.desc: The Fermi Paradox asks the ultimate question: Given a few reasonable assumptions about the chance of life arising elsewhere in the universe and the distance between the stars, why has an alien civilization not presented itself?

channel.desc: There is no such thing as the “perfect crime.” Find out why on Forensic Files, where real-life investigators piece together the evidence they need to solve grisly crimes, ripped straight from the headlines.

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico

programme.desc: (S1E8) After the DEA closes in on Rafa's enormous pot field, Félix tries to stop his associates from retaliating. Kiki and Jaime meet with investigators.

programme.sub-title: A mysterious mermaid appears? As consciousness fades away…

programme.sub-title: Fists full of emotion! Luffy unleashes gatling with all his might!
programme.desc: Luffy lies battered and badly beaten, but Usopp’s desperate pleas inspire the rubber-man to mount one final, furious attack on Rob Lucci!

programme.title: One Piece
programme.sub-title: From the sea, a friend arrives! The straw hats share the strongest bond!
programme.desc: With their leader crippled by exhaustion and their escape ship destroyed, the Straw Hats find themselves with only one treacherous option: throwing themselves into the sea!

programme.sub-title: Everyone makes a great escape! The road to victory is for the pirates!

programme.title: One Piece
programme.sub-title: Thank you, merry! Snow falls over the parting sea!
programme.desc: The Straw Hats bid a tearful farewell to the brave little ship that was their home for so very many adventures. Rest in peace, Merry!

programme.sub-title: The strongest family? Luffy's father revealed!
